Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:22.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Written by their thirst for destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:25.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We searched along the rails
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Hoping to find another trail
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Leading to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:36.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}The heavens are waiting for motion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:38.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Fired up for action
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}There's no gain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:40.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:42.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:43.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My pains don't exist to entertain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Count with me, one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:51.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many liters can you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many turns you plan to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many lives you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I saw a star
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Brightening up the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:12.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}So don't you stop my fires from burning our everything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:17.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}You and me are nothing but temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:22.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't you start begging for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}For when I win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I won't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:35.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Yes, I shall win your one-sided game
